&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;You serve as the consistent connective force between clients, creative teams, strategy, and&amp;nbsp;production, ensuring that work is insight-led, high-impact, and executed to the highest standard.&amp;nbsp;In this role, you are expected to lead both the what and the how: shaping the direction of your&lt;br&gt;accounts while developing and mentoring the team that makes the work happen.&lt;/p&gt;
