&lt;li&gt;Build strong, trust-based relationships with senior client stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and lead organic growth opportunities within accounts, helping to expand&amp;nbsp;Motive’s footprint.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regularly assess account health and collaborate with agency leadership to&amp;nbsp;evolve the partnership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensures all projects, products, marketing, and communications strictly adhere to&amp;nbsp;the specific creative requirements and restrictions of the nicotine industry. This&amp;nbsp;includes navigating regulations around product marketing, age verification, and&amp;nbsp;health warnings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic &amp;amp; Creative Direction&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate client goals and briefs into actionable strategic and creative&lt;br&gt;

