&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1nbwrcv&quot; data-start=&quot;2019&quot; data-end=&quot;2171&quot;&gt;Build and maintain strong relationships with senior client stakeholders, as well as key external partners (leagues, governing bodies, rights holders).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ct6dqf&quot; data-start=&quot;2172&quot; data-end=&quot;2289&quot;&gt;Serve as a trusted advisor, translating business objectives into impactful experiential and sponsorship strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;8tl2ac&quot; data-start=&quot;2290&quot; data-end=&quot;2362&quot;&gt;Represent Motive in a highly visible role on a marquee global program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
