&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ACCOUNT EXECUTIVE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an &lt;strong&gt;Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt; at Motive, you play a key role in the day-to-day execution of client work. You are the connective tissue between the client and our internal teams—responsible for driving projects forward, supporting strategic thinking, and ensuring work is delivered on time, on brief, and within budget.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a foundational role on the account team, offering exposure to a broad range of work including traditional, experiential, digital, promotional and media. You’ll collaborate with creative, strategy, brand experience and production, as well as other departments while continuing to grow your skills as a marketer, project manager, and client partner.&lt;/p&gt;
