&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who is equal parts strategist, operator and leader. Someone who loves bringing order to complexity, has strong opinions backed by curiosity, and gets excited about what&#39;s next.&amp;nbsp;If you&#39;re constantly saving campaigns, following creators, testing new platforms and thinking about how brands can participate in culture more authentically, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
