&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SR DESIGNER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div&gt;As a Senior Designer at Motive, you will help bring some of the world&#39;s most recognizable brands to life across a broad range of creative outputs. From integrated advertising campaigns and brand identity systems to packaging, digital experiences, experiential activations, live events, licensed products, and emerging platforms, you&#39;ll be challenged to create compelling work that connects with audiences in meaningful ways.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;We&#39;re looking for a highly conceptual, detail-oriented designer who thrives in a collaborative environment and is excited to tackle a diverse range of creative challenges. This role requires equal parts creative thinking, design craft, and executional excellence.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You will work closely with Creative Directors, Associate Creative Directors, Art Directors, Writers, Strategists, Account teams, Brand Experience teams, and Production partners to develop and execute breakthrough creative solutions across multiple brands and disciplines.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Areas of Responsibility&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Concept, design, and execute a wide variety of creative deliverables across branding, advertising, digital, brand experience, commerce, packaging, and content-driven projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of projects and design workstreams from concept through final execution, ensuring creative excellence at every stage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute meaningful visual ideas, design-driven thinking, and creative solutions during brainstorming and concept development sessions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Creative Directors, Art Directors, writers, strategists, account teams, and production partners to develop innovative and effective creative work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create thoughtful design systems and visual frameworks that can scale across campaigns, experiences, and brand touchpoints.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present work confidently to internal teams and clients, clearly articulating creative rationale and design decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple projects simultaneously while maintaining exceptional attention to detail and meeting deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance, feedback, and mentorship to junior designers when appropriate, helping elevate the overall quality of work across the team.&lt;/li&gt;
